_:Nd3b8997d02b143ebbb4c3192fd54fc64 <http://schema.org/description> "The Legal Services Board (LSB) ensures that regulation in the legal services sector is carried out in the public interest and that the interests of consumers are placed at the heart of the system. LSB is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Justice ." .
